{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In an alternate universe, Forklift Combat is the most popular sport by far. Forklifts all over the world watch as Forklifts battle for the ultimate title of Forklift Certification.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Fork up&quot; your friends in this exciting and hilarious online and local party game as you compete to get Forklift Certified in a wild, chaotic forklift battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FORK UP YOUR FRIENDS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience the game through online or local multiplayer - play on the couch or all cozied in your little gamer cave.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CHOOSE YOUR FORKLIFT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from a unique cast of Forklift characters to show off your flare... or goofiness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">WHAT THE FORK?!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use fun (and totally not dangerous) pick-up items and unique environment interactions to give you the upper hand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FORK IT UP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Master a tight, fluid movement system. Drift, fork, and clash your way to victory.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440600/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734290645","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440600/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1734290645","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440600/307f13cac9090dfb6facbe499f5247d60d6c8bad/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734290645","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440600/307f13cac9090dfb6facbe499f5247d60d6c8bad/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734290645","categories":[{"descr